title: Arthur, The Complete Season 15 (SD iTunes WEB-DL)
description:
Arthur, The Complete Season 15 (SD iTunes WEB-DL)

ARTHUR is an animated series aimed at the 4- to 8-year old viewer based on the children's books by Marc Brown. It's a show about growing up, exploring the world and finding your place in it. In each episode Arthur, an 8-year old aardvark, guides us through energetic, emotional stories that deal with real "kid issues" from a kid's point of view.

All episodes come from the iTunes Store, with all the iTunes metadata, and most of them with subtitles in CC format.

If you need to use this files as MP4s, change the extension.


Remember to share and enjoy!
